There is no single cause — it is the accumulation of many sequential steps, each adding latency. Here is every bottleneck found in the code.

1. Enormous Number of Sequential LLM API Calls
Every LLM call to OpenAI takes 2–15 seconds depending on prompt size and model. Count how many happen in a single deep-dive job:

