When the LLM generates Python code that fails (wrong column name, type error, import error), the pipeline:

Captures the error
Makes another LLM call: "Fix this code given this error"
Executes again
Repeats up to 3 times
For 10 EDA tasks + 3 hypothesis tests = 13 possible retry chains, each potentially tripling the time for that task.

6. Vision Analysis Is Rate-Limited to 3 Concurrent Calls
